  "prompt": "What NFL team has the most loyal fans?",
  "response": "Loyalty among NFL fans can be measured in various ways, such as attendance, social media engagement, and fan surveys. While it's subjective and can vary from year to year, the Pittsburgh Steelers are often cited as having some of the most loyal fans in the NFL. Known as \"Steeler Nation,\" their fans are renowned for their dedication, traveling well to support the team at away games and consistently filling their home stadium, Acrisure Stadium. Other teams with notably loyal fanbases include the Green Bay Packers, the New England Patriots, and the Dallas Cowboys.",
